---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---
<BaseLayout
  title="Media Kit — Brand Assets & Sponsorship"
  path="/media-kit/"
  description="Inlet Wire media kit. Brand statement, audience snapshot, logo pack, and sponsorship contact for BC-music-adjacent partners."
>
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Media kit</h1>
      <p class="lede">Brand statement, audience, assets, and ways to work together.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section>
    <div class="container prose stack-lg">
      <div>
        <h2>Brand statement</h2>
        <p>Inlet Wire is your direct line to BC artists. Each week, host Eric Chan sits down with an artist shaping the new sound of British Columbia. Listen in, and you are part of how the next wave of BC music gets heard.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2>Audience</h2>
        <p class="text-muted">Percentage snapshot, updated quarterly.</p>
        <p>Breakdown by geography, age, and platform is published here at the end of each quarter. Qualitative read: thoughtful local-music listeners in BC who want <a class="link" href="/episodes/">the story behind the song</a>, not a promo cycle.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2>Assets</h2>
        <p>Logo pack (PNG + SVG, monochrome variants) available on request. Email <a class="link" href="mailto:contact@inletwire.com?subject=Media%20Kit">contact@inletwire.com</a> with "Media Kit" in the subject.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2>Sponsorship and charity</h2>
        <p>Open to sponsorship conversations and charity work. Reach Eric at <a class="link" href="mailto:contact@inletwire.com">contact@inletwire.com</a>.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
